review: Visited this place with family. Had a very bad experience. Torn bedding, dirty broken furniture, dirty washrooms, and poor service. Spiders in room. Also there were spider webs in room. Only breakfast was OK, nothing else was OK. Not recommended at all..
name: Ankit A

review: If you want to have a good rest and stay close to the city of Rishikesh this is a good option, it's comfortable great space and privacy. You can find restaurants and travel agencies very close to organice your trip.
name: Holver A
